<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Brasil | Luan Especialista</title>

  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@500;600&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

  <style>
    *{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}

    html,body{
      background:#050505;
      color:#fff;
      font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;
      overflow-x:hidden;
    }

    a{text-decoration:none;color:inherit}

    .page{
      min-height:100vh;
      background:
        linear-gradient(to bottom,rgba(0,0,0,.62),#050505 76%),
        url("./imagens/brasil-hero.webp") top center/cover no-repeat;
    }

    .container{
      width:100%;
      max-width:1120px;
      margin:auto;
      padding:26px 22px 60px;
    }

    .top{
      display:flex;
      justify-content:space-between;
      align-items:center;
      margin-bottom:80px;
    }

    .logo{
      width:52px;
    }

    .whats{
      border:1px solid rgba(215,171,99,.45);
      color:#f0cc82;
      padding:11px 22px;
      border-radius:999px;
      font-size:13px;
      font-weight:700;
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.04);
    }

    .hero{
      max-width:650px;
      margin-bottom:90px;
    }

    .eyebrow{
      color:#d7ab63;
      font-size:12px;
      letter-spacing:4px;
      text-transform:uppercase;
      margin-bottom:18px;
      font-weight:700;
    }

    h1{
      font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;
      font-size:clamp(46px,7vw,82px);
      line-height:.94;
      font-weight:500;
      margin-bottom:24px;
    }

    .gold{color:#d7ab63}

    .hero p{
      color:rgba(255,255,255,.78);
      font-size:17px;
      line-height:1.7;
      max-width:520px;
      margin-bottom:32px;
    }

    .cta-row{
      display:flex;
      flex-wrap:wrap;
      gap:14px;
      align-items:center;
    }

    .primary-btn{
      display:inline-flex;
      align-items:center;
      gap:10px;
      background:#d7ab63;
      color:#070707;
      border-radius:999px;
      padding:15px 26px;
      font-size:13px;
      font-weight:800;
      text-transform:uppercase;
      letter-spacing:.5px;
    }

    .secondary-btn{
      color:#e8c27a;
      font-size:13px;
      font-weight:700;
      padding:15px 8px;
    }

    .section-title{
      margin-bottom:26px;
    }

    .section-title span{
      color:#d7ab63;
      font-size:12px;
      letter-spacing:4px;
      text-transform:uppercase;
      font-weight:700;
    }

    .section-title h2{
      font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;
      font-size:clamp(34px,4vw,52px);
      font-weight:500;
      margin-top:10px;
    }

    .paths{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);
      gap:22px;
      margin-bottom:34px;
    }

    .path-card{
      min-height:420px;
      border-radius:28px;
      overflow:hidden;
      position:relative;
      background-size:cover;
      background-position:center;
      border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.12);
      display:flex;
      align-items:flex-end;
    }

    .path-card::before{
      content:"";
      position:absolute;
      inset:0;
      background:linear-gradient(to top,rgba(0,0,0,.88),rgba(0,0,0,.38),rgba(0,0,0,.08));
    }

    .path-content{
      position:relative;
      z-index:2;
      padding:28px;
      width:100%;
    }

    .path-content h3{
      font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;
      font-size:38px;
      line-height:1;
      margin-bottom:14px;
    }

    .path-content p{
      color:rgba(255,255,255,.78);
      font-size:15px;
      line-height:1.6;
      max-width:390px;
      margin-bottom:22px;
    }

    .glass{
      background:rgba(8,10,12,.68);
      border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.10);
      backdrop-filter:blur(14px);
      border-radius:22px;
      padding:24px;
    }

    .how{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:1.1fr 2fr;
      gap:24px;
      margin-top:30px;
      margin-bottom:34px;
    }

    .how h2{
      font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;
      font-size:38px;
      font-weight:500;
      line-height:1.05;
    }

    .steps{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);
      gap:16px;
    }

    .step{
      padding:22px;
      border-radius:20px;
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.045);
      border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.09);
    }

    .step strong{
      color:#d7ab63;
      font-size:12px;
      letter-spacing:2px;
    }

    .step h4{
      margin:12px 0 8px;
      font-size:17px;
    }

    .step p{
      color:rgba(255,255,255,.68);
      font-size:13px;
      line-height:1.55;
    }

    .final-cta{
      border-radius:28px;
      padding:34px;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at right,rgba(215,171,99,.16),transparent 36%),
        rgba(255,255,255,.055);
      border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.10);
      display:flex;
      justify-content:space-between;
      align-items:center;
      gap:24px;
    }

    .final-cta h2{
      font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;
      font-size:36px;
      font-weight:500;
      line-height:1.08;
    }

    .final-cta p{
      color:rgba(255,255,255,.68);
      margin-top:10px;
      max-width:530px;
      line-height:1.6;
    }

    @media(max-width:850px){
      .container{
        padding:22px 16px 46px;
      }

      .top{
        margin-bottom:64px;
      }

      .logo{
        width:48px;
      }

      .whats{
        display:none;
      }

      .hero{
        margin-bottom:66px;
      }

      .hero p{
        font-size:15px;
      }

      .paths{
        grid-template-columns:1fr;
      }

      .path-card{
        min-height:360px;
      }

      .path-content{
        padding:22px;
      }

      .path-content h3{
        font-size:34px;
      }

      .how{
        grid-template-columns:1fr;
      }

      .steps{
        grid-template-columns:1fr;
      }

      .final-cta{
        flex-direction:column;
        align-items:flex-start;
        padding:26px;
      }

      .final-cta h2{
        font-size:32px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <main class="page">
    <div class="container">

      <header class="top">
        <a href="./index.html">
          <img class="logo" src="./imagens/logo.png" alt="Luan Especialista">
        </a>

        <a class="whats" href="https://wa.me/5547992120915?text=Quero%20entender%20as%20possibilidades%20patrimoniais%20no%20Brasil">
          Falar com especialista →
        </a>
      </header>

      <section class="hero">
        <div class="eyebrow">Estratégias patrimoniais para o Brasil</div>

        <h1>
          O brasileiro comum financia.<br>
          <span class="gold">O estratégico constrói patrimônio.</span>
        </h1>

        <p>
          Existem caminhos mais inteligentes para sair do aluguel, estruturar patrimônio
          e transformar planos em possibilidades reais no Brasil.
        </p>

        <div class="cta-row">
          <a class="primary-btn" href="https://wa.me/5547992120915?text=Quero%20entender%20as%20possibilidades%20para%20construir%20patrimônio%20no%20Brasil">
            Entender possibilidades →
          </a>

          <a class="secondary-btn" href="#cenarios">
            Ver cenários ↓
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="cenarios">
        <div class="section-title">
          <span>Escolha seu momento</span>
          <h2>Qual cenário faz mais sentido para você hoje?</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="paths">

          <article class="path-card" style="background-image:url('./imagens/sairdoaluguel.png')">
            <div class="path-content">
              <div class="glass">
                <h3>Sair do aluguel</h3>
                <p>
                  Para quem quer parar de pagar por algo que nunca será seu
                  e começar a estruturar o primeiro patrimônio.
                </p>
                <a class="primary-btn" href="https://wa.me/5547992120915?text=Quero%20entender%20possibilidades%20para%20sair%20do%20aluguel">
                  Quero entender →
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="path-card" style="background-image:url('./imagens/kitnets.png')">
            <div class="path-content">
              <div class="glass">
                <h3>Construção patrimonial</h3>
                <p>
                  Para quem pensa em renda, kitnets, imóveis e construção
                  de patrimônio com visão de longo prazo.
                </p>
                <a class="primary-btn" href="https://wa.me/5547992120915?text=Quero%20entender%20construção%20patrimonial%20com%20kitnets%20e%20imóveis">
                  Ver estratégia →
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>

        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="how glass">
        <div>
          <div class="eyebrow">Como funciona</div>
          <h2>Uma conversa para entender o melhor caminho.</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="steps">
          <div class="step">
            <strong>01</strong>
            <h4>Momento</h4>
            <p>Entendemos se você busca sair do aluguel, investir ou construir patrimônio.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="step">
            <strong>02</strong>
            <h4>Estratégia</h4>
            <p>Organizamos possibilidades de acordo com sua realidade e objetivo.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="step">
            <strong>03</strong>
            <h4>Direção</h4>
            <p>Você recebe um caminho mais claro antes de tomar qualquer decisão.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="final-cta">
        <div>
          <h2>Quer entender qual caminho faz sentido para você?</h2>
          <p>
            Fale diretamente comigo no WhatsApp e me diga se o seu momento é sair do aluguel
            ou construir patrimônio.
          </p>
        </div>

        <a class="primary-btn" href="https://wa.me/5547992120915?text=Quero%20entender%20qual%20estratégia%20patrimonial%20faz%20sentido%20para%20mim">
          Falar no WhatsApp →
        </a>
      </section>

    </div>
  </main>

</body>
</html>
